{"tid":1046214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家呢一刻真係好難過⋯⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-03-04T05:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T08:28:32.000Z","uid":124558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fc80dcde534dd578dea344b98b1a70a3e784f0","tid":1046214,"uid":124558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"2019年開始就係惡夢嘅發生⋯<br />\n以為好穩陣嘅工就黎完約唔續<br />\n以為好穩陣拍咗幾年拖 一下子分咗手<br />\n以為情況穩定嘅好親嘅親人突然走埋<br />\n<br />\n以為捱過一件事只要正面積極就會好返，點知係一次比一次大嘅打擊。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我真係覺得好難過，點解咩都係同一時間發生，一d抖氣嘅位都唔比我⋯我知我嘅事係冰山一角，但我真係好辛苦好難接受一個又一個嘅惡耗"},{"pid":"93c944de57b411b2d51b42e34f43b452ffef137f","tid":1046214,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"💪💪💪"},{"pid":"8e7aa91608d7676c3e041077d39317c867fba4d6","tid":1046214,"uid":193193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"了解"},{"pid":"e0eed49df86dd50209abd450959bd80cc349cd5d","tid":1046214,"uid":78018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"堅強"},{"pid":"74e640253538448b78f1df5f5b8e7120d3d6513a","tid":1046214,"uid":208499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"4c630e130d71a1df328ba00fed28a234b857640a","tid":1046214,"uid":233485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"支持住啊"},{"pid":"689820f30a8e65b33891620f1b29224d34acb9f2","tid":1046214,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟"},{"pid":"db4bf43961099a462965da8759b74d77bd6e8576","tid":1046214,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"撐住呀巴打<br />\n過咗就有好日子㗎啦"},{"pid":"28e814c3c4280000244a902996d6c6b80f10ff01","tid":1046214,"uid":214416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"你要對自己好啲先會開心啲"},{"pid":"103750411